{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dohd man mannas See-\nwäs nnmannus Behrnus/ kadeht\nes tew kalpojis eſimu / tad es ee-\nschu / jo tu gann finni to Kalpo-\nfchami/ar fo es tew eſimu kalpojis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lahbans fazztja us to:\nJa es luhsams/ Schehlastibu ef-\nmu atraddis tawãs Azzis/ es ef-\nimu noprattis / ka tas KUNGS\nmann tewis deht irr fivehtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazztja wiꞥſch : praf-\nſi to Algu / tad es to dohſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazztja us winnu :\ntu finni/ ka es tew eſimu kalpojis/\nun ka tawi Lohpi pee man irr\nbijufschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo preefsch mannim tew\nbij Maggums / un tas irr leelã\nPulka wairojees / un tas\nKUNGS irr tew fivehtijs zaur\nmannu Kahju / un nu / kad buhs\ntad man fawu Namnu apgah-\ndaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazztja : ko es\ntew dohſchu? tad fazztja Jehkabs/\ntew ne buhs man ne neeka doht/ ja\ntu man scho Leetu darrifi/ tad es\natkak gannifchn/un fargaschn ta-\nwas Awis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es isttaigaschu fchodeen\npa wiﬀu tawn Gannamu-Pul-\nku / un atschkirſchu no turrenes\nwiﬀus raibus/ un lahfainus Loh-\npus / un wiﬀus mellus Lohpus\nstarp teem Jehreim / un wiﬀus\nlahfainus/ un raibus/starp tahm\nKasahm / un tahs buhs man par\nAlgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atbildēhs manna Ta-\nſniba/ jeb fchodeen jeb rihtu / ka-\ntu nahkti pahr mannu Algu/ ka-\npreefsch tawahm Azzim / wi-\nkas ne irr raibs / un lahfainus\nstarp tahm Kasahm / un mele-\nstarp teem Jehreem / to buhfch-\nes ſadsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazztja Lahbane-\nRedſt / Mannis pehz lai tas i-\npehz tawu Wahrdü.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas atschkihre tan-\nDeenã tohs lahfainus/ un raib-\nAhschus/ un wiſkas lahfainas/ u-\nraibas Kasas/ wiﬀu/ pee ka Ba-\ntuns bija/ un wiſs / kas me-\nbija / starp teem Jehreem / wi-\nwiſch eedewe tohs fawo Be-\nnu Rohkã.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fchkihrabs trejo Dee-\nGahjumu starp few un sta-\nJehkabu / un Jehkabs gann\nLahbana zittas Awis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Jehkabs Ri-\nstes no falteem Peppekeem /\nLasda-Kohkeem/un Kastano-Ri-\nkeem / un rohbija eekſch teem bi-\ntus Rohbus / nomisodams\nBaltumn / kas wirs tahm Ri-\nstehm bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch likke tohs Ri-\nzinus / ko wiꞥſch bij misceis/u-\ndens-Sillês/un Dserama-Tr-\nkõs tahm Awim preefscha/ kata-\ndsert nahkdamas apeetohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs Awis apgahja-\npahr tahm Rihkstehm / un w-\ndahs eeraihas / lahfainas /\nraibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs atschkihre te-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
